### Bull Case
✅ Best-performing S&P 500 stock with accelerating revenue growth (53.5% guided)  
✅ **U.S. commercial revenue up 93% YoY** — proof that AIP is a genuine enterprise phenomenon  
✅ Massive, unassailable moat in government/defense with 20+ year relationships  
✅ **$10B Army contract** provides long-term revenue visibility  
